  "description": "R5: `Provenance.entity.role`",
  "purpose": "This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the\r\nelement `Provenance.entity.role` as defined in FHIR R5\r\nin FHIR R4.\r\n\r\nThe source element is defined as:\r\n`Provenance.entity.role` 1..1 `code`\r\n\r\nAcross FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:\r\n*  R5: `Provenance.entity.role` 1..1 `code`\n*  R4B: `Provenance.entity.role` 1..1 `code`\n*  R4: `Provenance.entity.role` 1..1 `code`\r\n\r\nFollowing are the generation technical comments:\r\nElement `Provenance.entity.role` is mapped to FHIR R4 element `Provenance.entity.role` as `SourceIsBroaderThanTarget`.",
